<DocsLayout title="Overview">
  <h1>Anta Design System</h1>
  <p>
    Anta is a portable UI component library built on a two-tier architecture:
    web components provide the rendering layer, and JSX wrappers provide a typed
    component API for React and Preact.
  </p>
  <p>
    The design system follows a <strong>component-token-first</strong> philosophy.
    Each component defines its own CSS custom properties rather than depending on
    a global token system.
  </p>

  <h2>Getting started</h2>
  <p>Import components from the <code>anta</code> package and register the custom elements:</p>

  <pre><code set:html={`import { Progress } from '@antadesign/anta'\nimport '@antadesign/anta/elements'`} /></pre>
</DocsLayout>
